data.text:
Most everyone here lives in the neighborhood. We'll have immunity in two weeks. 
All of this is to say that May 14th will be LIT in my neighborhood. /end

The clinic opened at 9. When I got here at 8:45 (foolishly thinking the 2nd dose line would be short), there were several hundred people in line for each vaccine, wrapping around the block in opposite directions. 2/
